Tickets Available Now For Our New Season
﻿
Tickets Available Now For Our New Season!
Check out our complete list of upcoming & past live shows for LaBelle, FL and the surrounding area’s residents and guests. We’ve got a little bit of something for everyone’s entertainment taste – from country music to southern rock, comedy shows to rockabilly. You don’t want to miss out on the fun!
Food Truck will be on location 90 minutes before each performance!
Our 2025 Season Lineup
Buy Tickets Now!
Creedence Clearwater Revival Tribute
Monday 7:00 pm
January 13, 2025
Join us on this musical odyssey, a journey that transcends time and space.Let the melodies of HEY TONIGHT Creedence Tribute Show remind you of the unbreakable bond between music and emotion.
Buy Tickets Now!
The Motown Soul Experience
Monday 7:00 pm
January 27, 2025
Experience the golden era of soul music with this passionate performances The purpose of this show goes beyond performing; it's about recapturing the unforgettable magic of Motown that will bring back memories of “the good old days” when music spoke to each of us!
Buy Tickets Now!
7 Bridges
Eagles Tribute Band
Sunday 6:00 pm
February 16, 2025
A stunningly accurate tribute, 7 Bridges is a group of extraordinary musicians who faithfully recreate and honor the soul stirring magic of one of rock's greatest legends. With each note they play and every lyric they sing, they pay homage to the unforgettable classics that have woven themselves into the fabric of our lives.

Bringing the Entertainment to You!
For quite some time now, LaBelle FL has had an overwhelming need for really GOOD entertainment options. LaBelle Entertainment started with the simple idea of bringing quality entertainers to the LaBelle and surrounding areas for local residents and visitors to enjoy. We have partnered with a great venue with a relaxed, casual atmosphere and a great list of events showcasing a wide variety of entertainment genres.
There’s something for everyone and now you don’t need to drive an hour away any longer. We’re bringing the entertainment to you!
